#: man-labplot.1.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot 2.6"
msgstr "LabPlot 2.6"

#. Tag: productname
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot"
msgstr "LabPlot"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"

#. Tag: refname
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>labplot</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>labplot</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"an application by KDE for interactive graphing and analysis of scientific "
"data."
msgstr ""
"aplikacija KDE za interaktivno risanje grafov in analizo znanstvenih "
"podatkov."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>labplot</command> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>LabPlot options</"
"replaceable></arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>file</replaceable></arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>labplot</command> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>Možnosti "
"LabPlot</replaceable></arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>datoteka</"
"replaceable></arg>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot is a data plotting and analysis tool."
msgstr "LabPlot je orodje za risanje in analizo podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Its features include 2D and 3D data and function plotting, easy editing of "
"plots, analysis of data and functions, support for different worksheets "
"using MDI and LabPlot project files."
msgstr ""
"Njegove zmožnosti vključujejo 2D in 3D podatke in risanje funkcij, enostavno "
"urejanje grafikonov, analizo podatkov in funkcij, podporo za različne "
"delovne liste z uporabo projektnih datotek MDI in LabPlot."

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note that LabPlot is called using <command>labplot</command>."
msgstr "Upoštevajte, da se LabPlot kliče z <command>labplot</command>."

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot options"
msgstr "Možnosti LabPlot"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a full summary of generic options, run <userinput><command>labplot</"
"command> <parameter>--help</parameter></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Za popoln povzetek splošnih možnosti zaženite <userinput><command>labplot</"
"command> <parameter>--help</parameter></userinput>."

#. Tag: option
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "--no-splash"
msgstr "--no-splash"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not show the splash screen."
msgstr "Ne prikaži pozdravnega zaslona."

#. Tag: option
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "--presenter"
msgstr "--presenter"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start in the presenter mode."
msgstr "Začni v načinu predstavitelja."

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arguments"
msgstr "Argumenti"

#. Tag: option
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "file"
msgstr "datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location of the project to be opened, usually ending with <literal role="
"\"extension\">.lml</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Lokacija projekta, ki ga želite odpreti, običajno s končnico <literal role="
"\"extension\">.lml</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The project file can be also compressed, with its filename ending with "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.lml.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">."
"lml.bz2</literal> or <literal role=\"extension\">.lml.xz</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Projektno datoteko je mogoče tudi stisniti, pri čemer se njeno ime datoteke "
"konča z <literal role=\"extension\">.lml.gz</literal>, <literal role="
"\"extension\">.lml.bz2</literal> ali <literal role =\"razširitev\">.lml.xz</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "Poglejte tudi"

#. Tag: member
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Full user documentation is available through the KDE Help Centre. You can "
"also enter the URL <ulink url=\"help:/labplot\">help:/labplot</ulink> "
"(either enter this <acronym>URL</acronym> into &dolphin;, or run "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/labplot</"
"parameter></userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Celotna uporabniška dokumentacija je na voljo v centru za pomoč KDE. Vnesete "
"lahko tudi URL <ulink url=\"help:/labplot2\">help:/labplot</ulink> (bodisi "
"vnesite ta <acronym>URL</acronym> v &dolphin; ali zaženite "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter </command> <parameter>help:/labplot2</"
"parameter></userinput>)."

